 <span data-ttu-id="e9d1e-105">处理<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>返回值<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A>属性由语音合成实现<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A>类方法派生自<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9d1e-105">Processing of the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> value returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property is handled by a speech synthesizes implementation of the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> method on a class derived from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span></span>  



## Examples  
